		<h1>Welcome to the Game of Googol!</h1><br>
		<p>The Game of Googol is a guessing game where you will have an amount of different numbers hiddden from you.<br> 
		The goal is to reveal the highest number in the group of hidden numbers. The catch is, the last number you reveal
		has to be your "guess." This means that you can't go back to a number you revealed before. If you can successfully
		reveal the largest number in the group and stop revealing new ones, then you win!</p>
